Homepage: https://gitlab.com/yphil/zapete

Package: zapete
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, xdotool
Description: Remote control for any computer in your local network
 Zapete is a remote control application that allows you to control your computer
 from any device on your local network using a web interface. It supports
 keyboard input, custom command buttons, and touchpad mouse control.
 .
 Features:
  - Web-based remote control interface
  - Customizable command buttons
  - Touchpad mouse control
  - Keyboard input simulation
  - Cross-platform support